  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IOReturnException
    Exception encapsulating IOReturn I/O Kit Error Return Values, defined as kern_return_t values in IOKit/IOReturn.h The return value supplies information in three separate bit fields: the high 6 bits specify the system in which the error occurred, the next 12 bits specify the subsystem, and the final 14 bits specify the error code itself.
